<note n="0199001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0199001">是毘闍耶王之弟。</note>
<note n="0200002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0200002">甘露飯王，是淨飯王之弟。</note>
<note n="0200003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0200003">協會本為溝那伽摩伽。</note>
